\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Installation
\f0\b0\fs24 \
To install Jamoma:\
	1. Install the most recent version of MaxMSP 4.2\
	2. Install the most recent version of Tap.Tools\
	3. Move the folder "Jamoma API" into /Library/Application Support/SiliconPrairie/\
	4. Move the folder "Jamoma Modules" into /Library/Application Support/SiliconPrairie/\
	5. Move the patch "Jamoma Init" into the Max Startup folder
