\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Technical Requirements - OS X (Minimum)
\f0\b0\fs24 \
- Apple Macintosh G3/700MHz, G4/500MHz Processor (or faster)\
- 512MB of RAM\
- Mac OS X version 10.2.3 or higher\
- Monitor set to a resolution of 1024 x 768 (preferred) or higher\
- Currently Supported Max Versions: 	Max 4.2 beta 12 for Mac OS X\
- Required Tap.Tools Version: 1.2.9 for Mac OS X		\
- Required Jitter Version: 1.1 beta 4 for Mac OS X\
\

